OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FA mother from has accused the local
OL,8,Fauthority of "turning their backs" on
OL,9,Fchildren with additional learning
OL,10,Fneeds (ALN) over her daughter's wait
OL,11,Ffor a space at Ysgol Heol Goffa.
OL,13,FThe ALN school was until recently
OL,14,Fexpecting a new building to increase
OL,15,Fcapacity but scrapped the plans due to
OL,16,Fbudget constraints.
OL,18,FThe council say they "are fully
OL,19,Fcommitted to providing the very best
OL,20,Ffacilities for your children and all
OL,21,FALN pupils in ."
