OL,7,FRebecca Davies' three-year-old
OL,8,Fdaughter, Millie, is autistic and has
OL,9,Fsevere learning difficulties.
OL,11,FShe believes Ysgol Heol Goffa is the
OL,12,Fbest place for her daughter to learn
OL,13,Fbut had been told she faces a wait of
OL,14,Fup to three years to get a place.
OL,16,FRebecca, a teacher herself, has had to
OL,17,Fgive up her job to stay at home with
OL,18,FMillie.
