OL,7,FShe told ITV Wales: "My other
OL,8,Fdaughter, who's neurotypical, in a
OL,9,Fmainstream school. It's state-of-the-
OL,10,Fart and she got in when she was
OL,11,Fsupposed to.
OL,13,F"The frustrating thing, for me, is all
OL,14,Fyou hear is 'early intervention is key
OL,15,Fto the progress that they make'.
OL,17,F"It feels like the world's best kept
OL,18,Fsecret because what is this 'early
OL,19,Fintervention? Because all I see is
OL,20,Fwaiting lists, queues and excuses."
