OL,7,F'Bursting at the seams'
OL,9,FPlans to move the school to a new
OL,10,Fbuilding were originally touted in
OL,11,F2017 and were expected to cost #12
OL,12,Fmillion.
OL,14,FThe planned relocation would have
OL,15,Fincreased capacity of the school from
OL,16,F75 to 120 pupils.
OL,18,FThe Council say the 'footprint' of the
OL,19,Fbuilding has been extended already,
OL,20,Fmeaning the original capacity of the
OL,21,Fschool has increased.
