OL,7,FRebecca said: "Ysgol Heol Goffa has
OL,8,Fcapacity for 75 pupils. At the moment
OL,9,Fthere's 124, so it's bursting at the
OL,10,Fseams.
OL,12,F"This is a building that, 10 years
OL,13,Fago, it was declared 'not fit for
OL,14,Fpurpose'. 10 years later, after bring
OL,15,Fpromised a new school and being told
OL,16,Fit's a priority, we've had the plug
OL,17,Fpulled.
OL,19,F"And to find that out on social media,
OL,20,Fyou just can't believe it."
